---
title: Savoury Tofu and Veggie Stir-Fry with Cashews and Garlic Rice
description: For those who don't shy away from spice, this tofu stir-fry packs a flavour punch and plenty of heat thanks to our Szechuan-style sauce! Toasted cashews finish off this dish for a culinary home run!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/saute-de-tofu-et-de-legumes-savoureux-7e887933.jpg
